{"tid":1293331,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日九龍遊行，我體會到咩係We Connect","createTime":"2019-07-07T15:40:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T15:56:26.000Z","uid":146277,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6e57809bcf4a41f63498310ecc16524342b78284","tid":1293331,"uid":146277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T15:40:32.000Z","msg":"遊行起步個陣，我同幾個大叔企咗係半島酒店個邊。有個大陸人着黑衫黑褲，拎住標語撥涼咁行咗黎我隔離同人video call，大概係講呢度超級多人。之後我就搭嗲問佢<br />\n<br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你知唔知呢度做緊咩呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：唔知呀，好多人呀！我行唔到入海旁呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我哋係到遊行反對修定逃犯條例呀！我哋由六月開始上街同政府講反對，但政府冇理過我哋，所以要繼續話俾政府知我哋要撤回修例！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：所以你哋係到圍政府（指住半島酒店）？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：唔係啦，政府總部係港島個邊，我哋去過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋會係唔同地方遊行，話俾政府知我地反修例！今日係由呢度行去高鐵個邊。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：啊 我今朝係個邊黎 。你係香港學生呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：係呀......普通話唔係咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我都知㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中 港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  connected<br />\n_____________________<br />\n<br />\n講完之後，前面有個戴咗帽、黑色眼鏡嘅大叔擰轉頭問我<br />\n<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  大叔：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你學生黎㗎？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：係呀（佢應該聽到曬我啲勁廢普通話）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：嗱，你係學生呀，咁你覺得呢場運動會點樣完結呢？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：一係政府真係撤回.....好難講呀，都唔知政府跟住會點做...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後我同佢一路行一路傾計，佢講返以前政府點點點，我講返而家啲年青人係呢場運動做咗啲咩...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：哦~你係00後，又冇BNO，2047年你先中年咋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：係呀，所以更加要行出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：而家啲大學學生會唔肯林鄭開會呀嘛，因為佢哋代表唔到所有示威者<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候大隊停咗係到，前面嘅婆婆聽到我地講緊啲咩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：係呀，同埋學生會林鄭滿足咗佢到嘅要求先呀，同埋之前林鄭搞囍帖街同天星碼頭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、婆婆：「係皇后碼頭呀！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：啊！係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，都係開會之後照樣推行，所以今次學精咗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：就係咁先話佢 好打得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就係咁，我同大叔由起點講到終點，當我諗住散水走人嘅時候<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你趕唔趕住返屋企呀？不如一齊去M記食啲嘢呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：啊...都得嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你唔嫌棄我呢個老人家係咁同你講嘢呀嘛，我都想update下而家啲年輕人諗咩呀。<br />\n我後生個陣覺得啲老人家好固執，到而家我老咗，唔知係身體機能問題定咩，有時真係固執咗啲，我都成日提住自己唔好咁，所以咪想同你呢啲後生交流下。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去到M記部機到揀嘢食個陣，大叔除咗佢頂帽，露出咗佢濃密嘅白髮，仲話自己好有heart，呢餐我俾啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n___________________<br />\n原來有啲上咗年紀嘅好想知而家啲後生仔諗緊咩，會做啲咩。有時遊行見到佢哋叫口號、舉牌真係中氣十足，老當益壯。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上一輩 年輕人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  Connected<br />\n<br />\n唔係個個老人家都係廢老㗎，有啲仲醒過好多年輕人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人 加油！"},{"pid":"feda400bf5f411b9a007e65264ee34bc8688681c","tid":1293331,"uid":196099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T15:56:26.000Z","msg":"<strong>WeConnect<br />\n香港人大團結</strong>"}]}